            "title": "Free Shipping",
            "content": "<p>Free shipping on all items in the store.</p>\n<p>Delivered in 3 to 8 working days.</p>",
            "content_popup": "<h3>Shipping<\/h3>\n<p>We have overseas warehouses in Houston, Los Angeles, and New Jersey, and the delivery time is 3-8 business days. We only ship to 48 contiguous states and Washington D.C. within the US, excluding Alaska, Hawaii and Puerto Rico..<\/p>\n<p>Each order is delivered by a third-party provider (e.g. FedEx, UPS, Amazon) to the address you provide. Depending on the workload of the logistics company, the estimated delivery time is 5-10 business days (2 business days for order processing and 3-8 business days for delivery). In the event of force majeure, it will delay the processing of the order.<\/p>"
          }
        },
