            "icon": "<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" data-prefix=\"fal\" data-icon=\"shield-alt\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewbox=\"0 0 512 512\">\n    <path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M466.5 83.7l-192-80a48.15 48.15 0 0 0-36.9 0l-192 80C27.7 91.1 16 108.6 16 128c0 198.5 114.5 335.7 221.5 380.3 11.8 4.9 25.1 4.9 36.9 0C360.1 472.6 496 349.3 496 128c0-19.4-11.7-36.9-29.5-44.3zM262.2 478.8c-4 1.6-8.4 1.6-12.3 0C152 440 48 304 48 128c0-6.5 3.9-12.3 9.8-14.8l192-80c3.9-1.6 8.4-1.6 12.3 0l192 80c6 2.5 9.9 8.3 9.8 14.8.1 176-103.9 312-201.7 350.8zM256 411V100l-142.7 59.5c10.1 120.1 77.1 215 142.7 251.5zm-32-66.8c-36.4-39.9-65.8-97.8-76.1-164.5L224 148z\"></path>\n</svg>",
            "title": "30-days Return Guarantee",
            "content": "<p>Learn More.</p>",
            "content_popup": "<h3>Returns Policy<\/h3>\n<p>We have a 90-day return policy, which means you can apply for a return within 90 days of receiving the item.<\/p>\n<p>Non-Returnable Items: Used, Clearance, promotional, or custom-made items (unless defective), Return requests made after 90 days.<\/p>\n<p>If there is no quality problem, you need to bear the return cost yourself.<\/p>\n<p>To initiate a return, you can contact us at support@reibii.com. If your return is accepted, we will send you a specific return shipping label(only supported by FedEx) and instructions on how and where to send the package.<\/p>"
          }
